.Dd $Mdocdate: June 7 2010 $
.Dt CGFOUR 4 sparc
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm cgfour
.Nd 8-bit color frame buffer
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "cgfour0 at obio0 addr 0xfb300000 level 4" Pq "sun4/100 and sun4/300"
.Cd "wsdisplay* at cgfour?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
is a color frame buffer with overlay plane for the P4 bus
of sun4 class workstations.
.Pp
The
.Nm
driver interfaces the frame buffer with the
.Xr wscons 4
console framework.
It does not provide direct device driver entry points
but makes its functions available via the internal
.Xr wsdisplay 4
interface.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr wscons 4 ,
.Xr wsdisplay 4
